{"tid":2123950,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭月娥：不會貿然引用「禁足令」等極端舉措","createTime":"2020-07-25T04:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T06:13:02.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1a393e982fcc0b529c671656b5754d1fa20bd73d","tid":2123950,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T04:59:23.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥表示，近日本港的新型冠狀病毒確診個案不斷上升，但如非萬不得已，不會貿然引用極端舉措。她發文指，近日不斷有關於政府會實施「禁足令」的虛假訊息在網上流傳，指這些有如「宵禁」的措施影響深遠，須非常小心行事。目前看來，香港仍有進一步限制處所營業和減少市民出外的空間。她呼籲市民咬緊牙關，在未來一段時間堅守社交距離，減少外出，並亦再次呼籲商舖業主和企業僱主，與大家一起共渡時艱，如有需要，政府定當盡力配合。 <br />\n<br />\n對有人造謠感氣憤 <br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又指，中央近日應她要求，協助加大香港檢測能力，和改裝亞博成類似「方艙醫院」。她批評，別有用心的人藉此散播謠言，說成有內地醫療團隊到香港醫院提供診治，或把港人的基因樣本送回內地等，令人氣憤。 <br />\n<br />\n8月上旬每日檢測量可達5萬個 <br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，衛生防護中心和醫管局過去10日，每日平均進行超過1萬個新型冠狀病毒檢測，並按需要向私營化驗所購買服務，估計本港私營機構的檢測能力可達到每日不少於2萬個，有關部門正積極協助這些機構加大能力，預計到下月上旬可達每日5萬個，並同時引進其他新檢測機構，目前已委託3間檢測機構為4類較高風險群組人士做病毒檢測，和外判部分檢測工作給私營化驗所。 <br />\n<br />\n她又指，警方利用超級電腦協助追蹤個案，由超過90名警員及後勤人員負責，包括有超過30名偵緝警務人員在衛生防護中心與衛生署人員合作。各警區亦會配合這些人員，盡快找出源頭及緊密接觸者，讓衛生防護中心更快跟進。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348900\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2348900&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxR9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=7815e853\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348900</a>"},{"pid":"a2cc34fae938ab9656d788ef3154aacc863e16a9","tid":2123950,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T04:59:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348900/林鄭月娥不會貿然引用禁足令等極端舉措\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2348900%2F%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E8%B2%BF%E7%84%B6%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8%E7%A6%81%E8%B6%B3%E4%BB%A4%E7%AD%89%E6%A5%B5%E7%AB%AF%E8%88%89%E6%8E%AA&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxR9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=9abde130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348900/林鄭月娥不會貿然引用禁足令等極端舉措</a>"},{"pid":"7258e92c6ed95beeb42be77259890bd3aec5d57f","tid":2123950,"uid":42700,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:00:07.000Z","msg":"佢呢頭話唔會<br />\n即係好快就實施"},{"pid":"feb997c97daf400e5fb0639a285aa8f9f50e0a11","tid":2123950,"uid":45376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:00:50.000Z","msg":"等睇中計"},{"pid":"60d27b15c8714287b1dc0664fa5c1a0e616df448","tid":2123950,"uid":19055,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:00:58.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">政府放毒，市民防疫<br />\n不如真攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"7019e3b5a2435ae968fef76b5acde32f6cf03c4f","tid":2123950,"uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:00:58.000Z","msg":"圈套<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a42fe186a94bb448dcaf67a343484bbb3be76f","tid":2123950,"uid":33471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:01:46.000Z","msg":"個套呢"},{"pid":"fd738fc67b7f42ca06b581199fd18bb600633667","tid":2123950,"uid":78515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:01:53.000Z","msg":"回力標<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462d3fc7b9970ecf95269c7196e6c3c860f0ae93","tid":2123950,"uid":99402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:02:12.000Z","msg":"佢無confirm個私營機構唔係中資wo"},{"pid":"ddf6d1744a0285b717136ef2f78d8df21b16f217","tid":2123950,"uid":297514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:02:32.000Z","msg":"即係好快就禁足令"},{"pid":"f61a7ad4b7b9a775a8e58229c5774ad534b6f83d","tid":2123950,"uid":255105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:04:55.000Z","msg":"次次講完即刻都被逼自打嘴巴，仲唔信邪？比著我就唔敢講到咁實啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99ed36db75aea6a562bab6cd88907ba68d3a0d6","tid":2123950,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:05:56.000Z","msg":"圈套 ready<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79bca507d3ceb4f363dcad94d87eb7e45ac94e7","tid":2123950,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:09:26.000Z","msg":"快啲用啦 唔好縮"},{"pid":"8140ceac0f8a72b78015fa086dfbbcd0a0eb533f","tid":2123950,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5029d609bca22fd6441715790241545aed722150","tid":2123950,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:22:07.000Z","msg":"禁足令？係咪重惡過宵禁呀？"},{"pid":"b5f9aeb479a5c7066d95e9a4da0c384c6fe7d628","tid":2123950,"uid":197163,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:23:53.000Z","msg":"其實佢知唔知醜，大家都係特別行政區，澳門把關咁果斷同成功"},{"pid":"06f3107827780bc273e7295ef38f90d149cdf66f","tid":2123950,"uid":204702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b5f9aeb479a5c7066d95e9a4da0c384c6fe7d628","tid":2123950,"uid":197163,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:23:53.000Z","msg":"其實佢知唔知醜，大家都係特別行政區，澳門把關咁果斷同成功"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:27:26.000Z","msg":"特首唔同 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f90b3056a3cf52e23d03e6b3c2a5ac82c56abd","tid":2123950,"uid":5420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:28:41.000Z","msg":"緊急法都用過啦 扮乜撚野"},{"pid":"8eeec89580af59bfeb95110da423ddb510e6384c","tid":2123950,"uid":62321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"姐係就黎會禁足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ae99ab6a93aabcbd242904ffd47f96011a8539","tid":2123950,"uid":321854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T06:13:02.000Z","msg":"2007 年，清拆灣仔囍帖街 15 人街頭行動被捕，引起社會反響，政府及後宣佈暫緩工程，派林鄭落場與居民商討，隔了一會，推土機就繼續如常開工，最後變了今日不輪不類的囍匯。<br />\n<br />\n2014 年林鄭被派出處理佔領運動與學生對話，及後透過中間人提出有第二輪會面。但然後再沒然後，擴日持久待民意消耗，就直接走數清場終結。<br />\n<br />\n一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而竭，林鄭是心明此道之人。公眾往往認為暫緩執行是釋出善意，其實對於一個執行政治任務的妹仔，今次再被派出處理政治炸彈，她很清楚所有的暫緩，都是為了打散群眾訴求無誤。<br />\n<br />\n如果多年來香港人見識過這個慣犯的慣技，每次都繼續盲目相信，那麼輸掉香港的理由就是你自己，與人無尤了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%85%E6%8B%86%E5%9B%8D%E5%B8%96%E8%A1%97-%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%A6%8B%E8%AD%98%E9%81%8E%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E7%9A%84-%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9-%E6%85%A3%E6%8A%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%258B%2586%25E5%259B%258D%25E5%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%2597-%25E4%25BD%2594%25E9%25A0%2598%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A6%258B%25E8%25AD%2598%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E7%259A%2584-%25E6%259A%25AB%25E7%25B7%25A9-%25E6%2585%25A3%25E6%258A%2580%2F&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxR9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=87c11c3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%258B%2586%25E5%259B%258D%25E5%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%2597-%25E4%25BD%2594%25E9%25A0%2598%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A6%258B%25E8%25AD%2598%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E7%259A%2584-%25E6%259A%25AB%25E7%25B7%25A9-%25E6%2585%25A3%25E6%258A%2580%2F&h=42791e1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%85%E6%8B%86%E5%9B%8D%E5%B8%96%E8%A1%97-%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%A6%8B%E8%AD%98%E9%81%8E%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E7%9A%84-%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9-%E6%85%A3%E6%8A%80/</a>"}]}